          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Elise designs Wild Mountain Child's products from her studio in Hazelbrook in the Blue Mountains. The Wild Tree Tools line is then hand-carved, hand-sanded, and hand-polished by Vietnamese artisans in a traditional craft village, using FSC-certified plantation Doussie wood and finished with food-grade oil. Fair Trade certified, the partnership supports work-from-home opportunities for young mothers and preserves ancient craft traditions passed through generations.</p>"
