        },
        "t2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>PlayFizz is Wild Mountain Child's own line of natural, no-waste fizzy sensory eggs, handmade in small batches in a studio overlooking the Blue Mountains. Coloured with organic plant-based dyes, scented with essential oils, and free of plastic and artificial additives, each egg bubbles and fizzes to reveal a tiny natural treasure inside. It is an open-ended sensory experience built for curiosity, with no chocolate wrappers, no plastic toys, and no waste.</p>"
          }
