        },
        "t3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>We curate Wild Mountain Child because their nature-play philosophy, FSC-certified materials, and partnership with Vietnamese artisans align with what we believe a toy should be: useful, beautiful, and gentle on the earth. Wild Mountain Child orders ship promptly with free shipping on orders $150 and over within the contiguous US. Returns are simple, and customer questions go to a real person on our team.</p>"
          }
