          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Browse the collection above for wooden sensory tools, mud-kitchen scoops and rolling pins, potion mixers, and PlayFizz sensory eggs. Wild Mountain Child pieces pair beautifully with felt play foods, peg dolls, and other natural-materials play that invites children outside, into the dirt, and into a slower kind of wonder.</p>"
